b) Bruna buys a car for £7500. The value of the car depreciates by x% each year. At the end of 2 years the value of the car is £4107. Work out the value of x.

## MARKING SCHEME
- M1: for a method to find the value after 1 year, eg $4500 \times 1.024 (= 4608)$ oe 
