- A1: accept 4775.37 (M2A0 is implied by 275.37 or 275.38. Correct answer not rounded to 2dp gains M2A0. SCB1 for 4770 or 4824 if M0 scored)
- P1: for a start to the process, eg $4107 \div 7500 (= 0.5476)$ (0.74 implies P1)
- P1: for a process to find percentage change eg $\sqrt{"0.5476"} \times 100 (= 74)$ or $(\sqrt{"0.5476"} - 1) \times 100 (= -26)$ or $1 - \sqrt{"0.5476"} (= 0.26)$ 
- A1: (a) 4775.38; (b) 26 

